Step 1: Prepare business application materials as required Prepare the following application materials: Email, Mobile phone number, Personal digital asset certificate (pictre), Digital asset transaction certificate (picture). Step 2: Submit the application Complete the merchant certification audit materials that need to be filled in and uploaded. Click Submit for Review. Step 3: Data Review We will review your business application information within 3-5 working days, please keep an eye on the review status, which can be viewed on the submission page. After approval, you can advertise in the fiat currency trading area. Agree to pledge 2000USDT as the merchant\'s security deposit. Please agree to freeze the deposit. How to apply to leave a business Step 1: Submit information Submit the corresponding account number and corresponding email address of the exiting merchant. Step 2: Submit the application When the corresponding data is completed, the corresponding application can be submitted. Step 3: Data Review We will process the withdrawal application you submitted within 2-3 working days, and we will refund the corresponding funds you pledged before. After the refund is successful, you will no longer have the corresponding merchant authority. You can go to the submission page to check the progress of the corresponding submission.
